CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 22,1958, page 42, reads: "Chatting With The Cook at Terrace House is Mrs. Calvin Bartlett. Mrs, Josie Price makes delicious meals for the patients at the convalescent home on Frankstown Ave. where they may enjoy peaceful hours of complete relaxation. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Josie Price wearing apron, cooking at stove, and Mrs. Calvin Bartlett wearing overcoat, in kitchen at the Harriet Tubman Terrace House for Convalescent Women and Girls
